    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car does show its age with some visible cosmetic wear, including minor scratches on the exterior and some thinning upholstery inside. You may notice some small fluid seeps typical for its mileage, and the suspension is a bit soft, but it remains safe and roadworthy. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has been maintained to keep it running well, even if it isn't the prettiest on the block.",
