      "description": "Hey guys! Honestly, it breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, garage-kept, and drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
